The shared-mime-info package contains the core database of common types and the *update-mime-database* command used to extend it.  It requires glib2 to be installed for building the update command.  Additionally, it uses intltool for translations, though this is only a dependency for the maintainers.  This database is translated at [[http://www.transifex.net/projects/p/shared-mime-info/|Transifex]].

See the [[Specifications/shared-mime-info-spec| Shared MIME Info Specification]] for more information about the database.

= git =

The [[GettingInvolved| git]] module for this spec is "shared-mime-info", in the "mime" repository. See [[http://cgit.freedesktop.org/xdg/shared-mime-info/| web interface]] for details

